Texture entry format:
<texture pack name/mod id>:<texture file>[:column[:row]]

Allowed faces:
    Front,    Back,    Left,    Right,    Top,    Bottom

Available blocks for ModBlockProvider:
BASE - standard block
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- Size (array)
- Textures (array) or Texture (single entry)

GRAY - standard, grayscale based block
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- Size (array)
- Textures (array) or Texture (single entry)
- Color (HSB, H and S values)
- Gray (array of grayed faces, array of ints, numbers from 0 to 5)

DIAGONAL - diagonal block (like sapling)
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- Size (array)
- Textures (array) or Texture (single entry)
- Color (HSB, H and S values)
- Faces

MULTI - multiple simple cube blocks
- Textures
- Ids (block data values)

FLAT - flat block
- Color (HSB, H and S values)
- Size
- Texture
- Face

CHEST - standard chest
- Texture
- IsLarge

TRAP_DOOR - trap door
- Texture
- Face

DOOR - simple door
- Textures (requires 2)
- Flip
- Face

TORCH - simple torch
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- Size (array)
- Textures (array) or Texture (single entry)

SLAB - simple slab
- Textures
- IsTop

STAIRS - stairs
- Textures

CROPS - crops
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- Size (array)
- Textures (array) or Texture (single entry)
- Delta

STEM - crop stem
- Textures

CUSTOM - fully custom block
- UsePitch
- UseYaw
- TextureColumns (array)
- TextureRows (array)
- Size (array)
- TexturesRes (array)
- Textures (array)
- Parts (sub section - block parts), 
  Each sub section has:
  - Pos
  - Size
  - Faces
